                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>She was taken before the justice, and there voluntarily confessed the fact.</p>
               <p>(The trunk was produced in court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I had some people I work for here yesterday to my character: they are not here now.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17810912-63-verdict316" type="verdictDescription">
